Arts + Culture,
Music


Jason Robert Brown

																																													Nov 18, 2024																										
								A renowned composer & lyricist, Brown’s accolades include Parade (Tony® winner, Original Score), The Bridges of Madison County (Tony® winner, Original Score and Orchestrations), 13, and The Last Five Years. Among upcoming pieces, star-studded collaborations and global performances with his band as a soloist, Brown now brings his cabaret notoriety to Pittsburgh for one night only.								READ MORE






